Class FeatureDetailsFragment

    EntitlementDetailFragment, PurchaseOptionDetailFragment

    public class FeatureDetailsFragment
extends android.app.Fragment
    A simple Fragment subclass. Activities that contain this fragment must implement the PercentageHolder interface to handle interaction events.
